name: The Temple of Earth's End
description:
Carter catches wind of an undiscovered Egyptian temple known as The Temple of Earth's End and sets off to find it. While searching, a hole opens up beneath him. As Carter regains his senses, he begins traversing these long tunnels when these tunnels begin collapsing in on themselves, chasing him. The gods aren't please with his presence.
